\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 60\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub On hearing it, many of his disciples\'a0said, \'93This is a hard teaching. Who can accept it?\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 61\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub Aware that his disciples were grumbling about this, Jesus said to them,\'a0\'93Does this offend you?
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 62\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub Then what if you see the Son of Man\'a0ascend to where he was before!\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 63\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub The Spirit gives life;\'a0the flesh counts for nothing. The words I have spoken to you\'97they are full of the Spirit
\fs15 \cf4 \super [\ul e\ulnone ]
\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub \'a0and life.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 64\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub Yet there are some of you who do not believe.\'94\'a0For Jesus had known\'a0from the beginning which of them did not believe and who would betray him.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 65\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub He went on to say,\'a0\'93This is why I told you that no one can come to me unless the Father has enabled them.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 66\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub From this time many of his disciples\'a0turned back and no longer followed him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1 \cf4 John 6\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What he SAID is what was offensive\'85not what He did.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want the ONLY thing that is offense in this service to be what is said\'85nothing else.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The interesting thing is the only group of people who had a problem with what Jesus was doing were the religious people!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not one non-Christian came up and complained at Jesus!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 We believe Good is the enemy of Great\
