\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 42\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub At daybreak, Jesus went out to a solitary place. The people were looking for him and when they came to where he was, they tried to keep him from leaving them.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 43\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \cf4 \nosupersub But he said,\'a0\'93I must proclaim the good news of the kingdom of God\'a0to the other towns also, because that is why I was sent.\'94\'a0
