\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 We believe Mission trumps Masonry\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t have a verse for this one\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Most of Jesus ministry was accomplished by meeting the needs of people and serving them.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His discipleship model was not to invite people to a church service and have them learn but have them do!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The question I\'92ve been asked before by some is \'91Ok Nic, when are we going to get our own building?\'92\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
