\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  Now I know the push back\'85I don\'92t believe in God\'85ok but do you believe there is right and wrong?  \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 Here is the issue:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are two choices \'96 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God is real or there is no God and we just sort of evolved over billions of years with no guidance\'85it\'92s all luck and chance.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Morality doesn\'92t make sense\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No one looks at a tiger and gets mad because it kills other animals\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}No one gets mad at a tiger for having multiple partners and kittens with them.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But we feel bad\'85we have a moral clause\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is anti-evolution\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Evolution says survival of the fittest - Morality says everyone is equal\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Evolution says do whatever to get ahead \'96 Morality says there are certain things you shouldn\'92t do\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Evolution says take whatever you want and do whoever you want \'96 Morality says things theft and rape are wrong\'85period.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
